OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA day of sunshine and well
OL,6,Fscattered, mostly light showers is
OL,7,Fexpected on Saturday. Feeling fresher
OL,8,Fthanks to a west to northwesterly
OL,9,Fbreeze, though pleasant when the sun
OL,10,Fappears.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FAfter a
OL,13,Fchilly start both Sunday and Monday
OL,14,Flook dry with light winds and some
OL,15,Fsunshine. A cooler northeasterly wind
OL,16,Fon Tuesday giving more cloud and the
OL,17,Fodd shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
